/seo\/international\/\"> site web international<i><\/i><\/a>, le choix de la structure d&#8217;URL est une \u00e9tape cruciale qui peut grandement influencer sa visibilit\u00e9 et son efficacit\u00e9 \u00e0 travers les diff\u00e9rentes r\u00e9gions du monde.<\/p>\n<\/div><div class=\"image-single-wrapper text-center\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" src=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/multilingue.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"Multilingue\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/multilingue.png 1920w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/multilingue-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/multilingue-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/www.noiise.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/multilingue-1536x864.png 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row el_class=&#8221;content-article article-table-matiere&#8221;][vc_column]<div class=\"text-bloc toc\"><p class=\"titre_3\">Table des mati\u00e8res<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_74 ez-toc-wrap-center counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">Sommaire<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColo